  "Metadata" -> {
   "built" -> "{2026, 4, 27, 15, 46, 31.003550}", 
    "history" -> {"14.2", "", "", ""}, "context" -> "QuantumMob`Q3`", 
    "keywords" -> {}, "specialkeywords" -> {}, 
    "tutorialcollectionlinks" -> {}, "index" -> True, "label" -> 
    "Quantum Mob/ Q3 Symbol", "language" -> "en", "paclet" -> "QuantumMob/Q3",
     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "DualSchurBasis[n, d] constructs the Schur basis for a system of n \
particles each associated with a d-dimensional Hilbert space, i.e., \
(\\[DoubleStruckCapitalC]^d) \\[CircleTimes]n. DualSchurBasis[content] \
returns the Schur basis of the permutation module associated with \\[Mu] = \
content, which is isomorphic to \\[CirclePlus]\\[Lambda] \
\\[RightTriangleEqual] \\[Mu] \\[ScriptCapitalY]^\\ \\[Lambda]\\[CircleTimes] \
\\[ScriptCapitalW]_\\[Mu]^\\[Lambda\\ ] , where \\[ScriptCapitalY]^\\[Lambda] \
is the space spanned by standard Young tableaux of shape \\[Lambda] and \
\\[ScriptCapitalW]_\\[Mu]^\\[Lambda\\ ] is the space spanned by Weyl tableaux \
of shape \\[Lambda] and content \\[Mu]. DualSchurBasis[shape, d] returns the \
Schur basis of \
\\[ScriptCapitalY]^\\[Lambda]\\[CircleTimes]\\[ScriptCapitalW]^\\[Lambda], \
where \\[ScriptCapitalY]^\\[Lambda] and \\[ScriptCapitalW]^\\[Lambda] are the \
irreducible representation spaces of the symmetric and unitary groups, \
respectively, associated with \\[Lambda] := shape. DualSchurBasis[shape, \
conent] returns the Schur basis of the space \
\\[ScriptCapitalY]^\\[Lambda]\\[CircleTimes] \
\\[ScriptCapitalW]_\\[Mu]^\\[Lambda\\ ].", "synonyms" -> {}, 
    "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "DualSchurBasis", "titlemodifier" -> "", 
    "metadescription" -> "", "windowtitle" -> "DualSchurBasis", "type" -> 
    "Symbol", "uri" -> "QuantumMob/Q3/ref/DualSchurBasis"}},
